This software has been written in two parts, gbridge_srv for the server which manage the IA and gbridge_cli which manage the IHM.

To compile and to build it perform in each subdirectory gbridge_*
./configure
make 
sudo make install


Principe of the game:
It is a bridge software where where train with prepared games (option File in the menu) or use a random number.
It is possible to fix the depth of the search in the IA. By default it is fixed to 5 (5 tricks) but it can been changed depending of your wish. 

 
